newsitem.title: USA: IMM Eurodollar futures finish short day lower.
newsitem.headline: IMM Eurodollar futures finish short day lower.

text.p: Dec 31 - IMM Eurodollar futures ended down in a short session, pressured by a slide in T-bonds after stronger-than-expected data earlier in the day. March Euros posted a double bottom at the one-week low of 94.43, but trade was very quiet after the initial sell-off. No trade Wednesday for the New Year's holiday.
